Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:14.35,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最後一頁開始看小說似的狂喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:21.53,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉と感情がリンクする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:21.53,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言與感情相互連接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.94,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛したい夜に濡れたいfor me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.94,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像熱戀那般對我發情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えないようにせめぎあう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不瞑目般地死纏爛打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:35.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪いたいのに遠回りをして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:35.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖想豪奪卻仍舊故作姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.09,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足りないlogic　溢れるtrick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.09,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不充分的邏輯　漫溢的詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.78,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えないように絡み合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.78,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁若無人地相互纏繞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:47.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もういっそこのままtRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:47.75,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了　乾脆就此沉眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.46,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.46,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:58.15,i,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 20 「覺醒」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎並不祗是想得到真神的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股容量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個世界一切的記錄者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就閉上嘴看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我記錄的世界沒了就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那就讓我來記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一切毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也將記錄到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股光芒 那就是靈王石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真 你一定能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步率和我見過的都不是一個檔次的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞所未聞的強大元神靈及其契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人要真神的力量做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給多點容量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了憎惡與怨恨的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真神的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怨念的聚合體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將再次融合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統治這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞爾小姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我們 先去看看那兩個人的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是容量的流動被暫時阻斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 黎真大人幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你 我也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的目標是獅子神大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓它們靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想碰大小姐一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒醒過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑的容量有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和揶雲打的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真破壞了靈王石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說它們是真神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既可以說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的憎惡和怨恨將天空染成了黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的怨念正在吞噬整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王石封印的恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對被封印那麼耿耿於懷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和你戰鬥我都做到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印的恐怕是真神本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而黎真也知道這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是從那一刻開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紋章是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女大人 請進行夢蔔儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子神巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 是怎麼樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 並不是不祥的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜聽我說 黎真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 小黑將被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 擁有那個紋章的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可母親您說看到的並不是不祥的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢到了能和真神對抗的人的降生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獅子神族傳承下來的Thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前和獅子神族的人訂立契約
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同與真神戰鬥的人用過的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她成了主根源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會擁有人類中最強大的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的降生 以及小黑的紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是真神降臨中的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 長老們並不想同真神作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要殺掉小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經控制不住長老們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是我們族得以從詛咒中解脫的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真 你要用雙手斬斷這不祥的因果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐是真神轉生這件事已經非常明確了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要殺掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情重復多少遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐不死 世界就要滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打倒真神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有能和真神對抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法保證打倒真神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果硬要阻止我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是少主我們也不會留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不贊成我們的行動 企圖讓大小姐逃跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能落此下場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要殺小黑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制住少主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王石的封印會在吸收了獅子神巫女的血後解開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 從真神的詛咒中解救我們的族人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真 你一定能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我離開清靜之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了母親夢見的能跟真神對抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備等她成為主根源後和她訂立契約
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然花了很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但通過制造主根源造成的容量暴漲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了通往蟲洞的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用連接所有靈石的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我破壞了全世界的所有靈石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我找到成了主根源並能和真神對抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了她的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立了契約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在真神完全復活前解開封印
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它擊倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真解開封印究竟有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼小黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獅子神大小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有確鑿的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒證據證明她是否會將我們引向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕 里央奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直是小黑在救你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的容量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐濃厚的容量流了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步加深了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 極限沖擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這果然是記錄中的那個紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒覺醒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個覺醒了 剩下的兩個也一定會復活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一在的詛咒就是小黑下的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股感覺是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一在的神 真神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是為了我開始的這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:46.10,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂ほし月の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:46.10,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光狂亂地灑向大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:53.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一恵み胸に受けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:53.29,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身體感受這上天的恩澤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:59.05,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌おう　歌おう　囁いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:59.05,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧　唱吧　輕聲唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:05.36,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踊ろう　踊ろう　一緒に　Pa.Dis.Thu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:05.36,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳吧　跳吧　一起　Pa.Dis.Thu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:17.14,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽ちた楽園で　契りを誓えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:17.14,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在枯朽的樂園締結誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:29.09,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀のドレス　月色に染まるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:29.09,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮服也染上了銀色的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真神施加在曾經打倒它的獅子神族上的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打倒的真神中的一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每數百年將在族人的身上轉生一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將斬斷這因果
